SUBENT        C3113001   20260315   20260420   20260420       C256
BIB                 11         15
TITLE      Behavior of nuclear projectile fragments produced in
            collisions of 14.5 A GeV 28Si with Pb and Cu targets
AUTHOR     (P.B.Price, Y.D.He)
INSTITUTE  (1USAUCX)
REFERENCE  (J,PR/C,43,835,1991)
FACILITY   (LINAC,1USABRK) Bevalac
SAMPLE     Two exposures with Pb (1.6 cm thick), Cu (1.0 cm thick)
            and detector modules (D1 to D4)
           . Exposure 1: D0-Pb-D1-Pb-D2-Pb-D3-Pb-D4
           . Exposure 2: D0-Cu-D1-Pb-D2-Cu-D3
DETECTOR   (TRD) Nuclear track-recording plastic sheets CR-39
ADD-RES    (ANGD) (1/theta)(dN/dtheta)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on the source of uncertainty
STATUS     (TABLE,,P.B.Price+,J,PR/C,43,835,1991) Table II
HISTORY    (20260315C) On
ENDBIB              15
COMMON               1          3
EN
GEV/A
 14.5
ENDCOMMON            3
